text: Discover the charm of this Craftsman-style home nestled on a spacious corner lot. Step onto the enclosed front porch and into a living room adorned with window seats, wainscoting, and gleaming fir softwood floors. The kitchen beckons with stainless steel appliances and a cozy eat-in cove. Retreat to the bathroom featuring a classic claw foot tub. From your backyard, soak in breathtaking views of Fidalgo Bay and Mt. Baker. Entertain under the pergola patio or let loved ones play freely in the fully fenced yard. Benefit from ample storage space below the home. With schools, restaurants, and shopping just a short stroll away, this residence offers unmatched convenience and character. Don't let this opportunity slip by!

Welcome to this mid-century home that offers many possibilities to the right buyer! The main level features a nice kitchen, dining and living room w/gas fireplace. On a clear day, enjoy a great view across the valley to the Olympic mountains. Two bedrooms, a full bath and a laundry area round out the main floor, which has wood floors and built-ins throughout. The lower level features many possibilities with another complete living areafull kitchen, comfortable family room w/ gas fireplace, bedroom, bonus room and a full bathroom. Outside is a private backyard with a spacious deck and a covered seating area. New roof installed 2023. The alley-accessed garage and great location near hospital and downtown make this an ideal investment.

Versatile multi-level home with custom touches throughout! Gorgeous main level living space features a cozy gas stove. The impeccable kitchen includes custom hickory cabinets, granite counters, black stainless appliances, and a dual fuel stove/range. Main level also offers a full bath and bedroom. The upper level has a spacious primary bedroom and bathroom. The lower level includes a bar area (future kitchen potential), space near the laundry room for storage (with future bathroom potential), bonus living room, and the 3rd bedroom. The newer detached shop is wired for water, sewer, natural gas, and EV charging. Expansive driveway for RV and vehicle parking. Large fully fenced backyard and a front yard with large flowering cherry trees.

This charming 1, 765 square-foot Craftsman-style home, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, is situated on just over a quarter-acre and is ready for new owners to call home. It includes two spacious living rooms, large windows that fill the space with natural light, and a cozy wood-burning fireplace for chilly days. The expansive master suite boasts a luxurious en-suite with a soaking tub and a walk-in closet. A small room at the top of the stairs is perfect for a den, craft room or nursery. The property also offers a two-car garage, large fully fenced private backyard with a massive deck, pond, and a storage shed. Beautiful custom sliding back door offers a pet door for the fur babies to have easy access to back yard.

This well maintained key turn ready home located in the desired Skagit Highlands is one that you don't want to miss! This 3-bed, 2.5-bath residence is packed with upgrades, including a brand-new furnace, AC Unit for the hot summer days, Stainless Oven, dishwasher, and a newer water heater which takes away the worry of replacing them in the near future. Stylish new light fixtures and ceiling fans add modern elegance. The fully fenced backyard offers a private area that is perfect for relaxation or entertaining. Enjoy parks and trails nearby, with easy access to the freeway, groceries, and restaurants. Don't waitschedule your viewing today and seize the opportunity to own this move-in-ready gem in a prime location!

This exceptional property offers the perfect blend of convenience, tranquility, & valley views. Situated on spacious acreage, it provides the ideal setting for peaceful living while being in town. The main home boasts a generous kitchen, a welcoming living room w/ a wood fireplace insert, & a bright sunroom. The lower level expands your living space w/ a large family room featuring a cozy gas fireplace insert, full bath, 2 additional finished rooms, & a walk-out patio w/ parking & separate entrance. In addition, a secondary manufactured home on the property is perfect for guests or a potential rental income opportunity. Transform this great home into your dream home on property that offers many possibilities.

This well-cared-for 3BR, 2BA single wide offers plenty of space & natural light in a great location, minutes from downtown Mount Vernon and medical plus walking distance to Haggen. No age restriction park has tons of street parking near unit for guests and great walkability. Ready for your cosmetic updates, this home has been lovingly cared for over the years and is in great condition. The siding has been recently painted giving a lovely curb appeal boost, and inside youll enjoy single-level-living with a generously sized kitchen and main living space. Your carport and shed are perfect for car and hobby storage. Must have park approval before submitting offers.

Move in ready! Nicely updated inside & out, top to bottom, in the town of La Conner! Too much to list here. Located within walking distance of all the shops, restaurants, water front, and everything else La Conner has to offer. Home features single level living and was completely gone through in 2019. New roof, new furnace, new Hardi Plank siding, new insulation in the crawl space & attic, kitchen & bathrooms were all remodeled, and the list goes on and on. Agent has a full list of the upgrades done. This home sits on a corner lot w/2 large storage sheds w/power, a covered car port that also has storage cabinets built in and extra room to park a boat or RV. City said it was possible to build a garage w/apartment. Buyer to verify all.

Charming updated 1954 home sits on .29 acres with some hint's of cabin styling. Open ceilings with sturdy beams, updated kitchen and bath. There is an east side sunroom that has a utility room adjacent. The sunroom is not part of the 888SF. Head accross the back yard and your will find a garage with work room and garage for the car. Behind the garage is a metal RV Cover that can keep your toys out of the weather. The back yard has an apple tree and space for a vegetable garden. A very private setting and access to the back yard, garage and Rv Cover via Azalea Lane. The home faces West and looks out to acres and acres of farmland. Super easy access to Hwy 20 and I-5. Schools, services, shopping and entertainment just minutes away.

Well maintained Lake Cavanaugh property with 3 buildings. Main house of 3066 sqft has upper-level suite w/office space, main level has kitchen, dining room, living room w/large wall of windows, fireplace, den/office/bedroom, fully finished rec-room that can be used as extra bedroom. The property features oversized 3-car garage that has a 480 sqft studio on top floor and it also connected to the main house 2nd floor deck. A tall garage-bay is ready for your car-lift or additional storage area. The cute beach front cabin has 2 bunk rooms, living room & kitchen area (no water hooked up) & deck overlooking the lake. The 60 beach front has patio, fire pit, dock & boat lift. Summer is here and the potential fun for this home is endless!

Enjoy prime in-town living and unmatched water views of Fidalgo Bay, Cap Sante Marina, and downtown Anacortes! This remarkable home features a 1, 000 sq ft deck for indoor-outdoor living, panoramic windows, vaulted ceilings, on a dead end road. The beautiful ensuite boasts exquisite finishes, creating a spa-like sanctuary and the primary closet includes a washer/dryer for convenient single-story living. Downstairs, you'll find a secondary kitchenette and a covered patio for year-round entertainment. The oversized lot offers space for a potential shop or ADU. Don't miss the large workshop with backyard access, perfect for any hobby or project! Truly rare to find a fully renovated home, located in town, with water views, on a large lot!
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Welcome to the Prairie Acres community! This lovely home with a charming wrap-around porch is the one you've been waiting for! The main level boasts a large living room with built-in shelving & a cozy wood stove. The formal dining area accommodates large gatherings & leads into a spacious kitchen with ample counter & storage space. Next to the kitchen is a large breakfast area, laundry/pantry & a sizable rec-room with a wet bar. The primary bedroom offers an ensuite bath & a walk-in closet. Additionally, there are two guest bedrooms & a full guest bath. Outside, a huge 2, 232 SF heated shop with an office awaits, along with a 432 SF multipurpose building. The 1.19-acres feature mature landscaping & space for your RV, tools & all your toys!

Unlock the potential of this spacious, vacant lot situated in the vibrant heart of Concrete, Washington. Nestled in a charming, small-town setting with stunning natural surroundings, this property offers a unique opportunity for your dream project or investment. Concrete is known for its picturesque landscapes and outdoor recreational opportunities. Make this your Next Home.

Classic updated mid century modern home! Unbelievable soaring vaulted living room ceiling, featuring a grand stone fireplace. With retaining the original features, there is new carpet, tile floors and light fixtures throughout. The large kitchen radiates lots of light, preserved cabinetry, new counters, sink, stove top, eating bar...and dining area. Huge oversized primary is en-suite w/remodeled bath, new tiled tub surround, counters and walk-in closet. Two nice sized bedrooms/remodeled guest bath. Wall of windows w/slider to patio and hot tub. Lets walk outside...entertain out back in the 14x16 gazebo surrounded by cedars, ferns, trails to the pond and cute little bridge! Just relax and meditate in the glam shed! Its magical! Fenced yard!

Gardener's paradise! Beautiful landscaping surrounds this charming 3 bedroom, 1 3/4 bath rambler in desirable Skyline neighborhood. Lots of natural light and great room feel. Open kitchen, dining area and living room with adjoining sunroom. Living room features a gas log fireplace and vaulted ceiling with a skylight. Sunroom opens to a spacious 2 level deck to enjoy the private, fully fenced gorgeous backyard and partial water view. Gas bbq hook-up on small patio. Even a fancy chicken coop! 1 car garage with good storage, workbench and EV plug in. RV parking with waste outlet in front graveled area. Close to Skyline amenities. Something for everyone!

Welcome to this charming, cozy Wildflower home! The large, bright, open living room features a vaulted ceiling and plenty of space to relax and unwind. The galley-style kitchen has a window and convenient oversized sink. Look out the window to a deck where you can enjoy your morning coffee! Primary bedroom has its own access to the bathroom that is shared in the hallway along with a second bedroom. A laundry room can also be found conveniently placed near the center of the home. The patio off the living room is great for entertaining and features space for seating and your own BBQ. The yard features garden space, a fire pit, and mature landscaping. A single car garage is located in walking distance. Come make this place your very own!

First time on the market in 54 years, this lovingly custom-built, immaculately maintained Westside Mount Vernon home is ready for new beginnings! Sitting on one beautifully landscaped acre in a peaceful neighborhood, a large, bright living room greets you upon entering the home, then flows nicely into the adjacent dining room. The tidy kitchen has a eating space & view of the great backyard. Also on the main floor are one bedroom, currently used as an office, a half bath, utility room & family room w/slider to the back patio. Upstairs are three bedrooms, a full bath, & a three-quarter bath off the primary bedroom. Note the three closets in the primary bedroom! Ample extra storage area at the top of the stairs and extra closets throughout.

Escape to a serene and peaceful retreat on 7.49 stunning acres, surrounded by nature's beauty. This property features an orchard with fruit trees, plenty of garden space, a dedicated camping area with cozy firepit, and a refreshing swim pondperfect for outdoor enthusiasts. The 2, 709 sq ft manufactured home offers 3 spacious bedrooms plus 2 additional bonus rooms with closets, unbelievable storage, wired for generator. A 3-car garage, additional shop plus plenty of space for your RV, boat and other toys! Wander through fields of dreams, under the shade of mature cedars, and discover the tranquility of country living!

Incredible multi-use property in serene setting w mountain views includes shop, barn, stable, equestrian space, & more. Spacious home features tons of windows, wood beam ceiling & hardwood floors throughout. Primary bedroom includes a barn door, huge slider to full length deck, walk-in closet, & spa like bath w dual waterfall sinks & soaking tub. Downstairs enjoy the built-in wet bar, cozy fireplace, & additional bedrooms. Outside enjoy the partially fenced yard w fruit trees, garden space, & expansive pasture. Plenty of space for your horses & other animals w shop, barn, stable, chicken condominium, & outbuildings. Detached garage & carport, & RV parking.

1886 sq ft one level home with 768 3-car attached garage on Fairway #9 at Skagit Golf and Country Club. Three bedroom home with 2 1/2 baths and great floor plan enjoys large windows, tons of natural light and golf course access and viewing pleasure. Abundant cabinets and counter tops in kitchen plus eating space along with a formal dining area. Enjoy sun and shade on great entertaining deck. Primary bedroom with walk-in closet, 3/4 bath and golf course view. 8-yr old roof, 3 yr old gas furnace. Large garage has plenty of room for the hobbyist, autos, golf cart and storage. Low maintenance landscaping includes a gazebo, vegetable garden and mature plantings.

Step into this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom rambler with a fully fenced backyard and a covered patio, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the serene surroundings of apple trees, berry bushes, and space for your own garden. The spacious primary bedroom boasts a large walk-in closet and a private bathroom, while the living area exudes a sense of openness with its vaulted ceiling. This property is conveniently located just minutes from schools, parks, and downtown Sedro Woolley, and offers easy access to I-5 for commuters. Nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac, directly across from the community park, this is the perfect place to call home.

Come and enjoy this spacious townhouse near downtown Anacortes! This home features vaulted ceilings, an open layout, and large windows for natural light. The main floor has a generous kitchen with shaker cabinets and ample storage. Welcoming everyone with a zero-step entry, plus a main level bedroom/bath for convenience Upstairs, enjoy the loft as an additional family room, and upper deck boasting views of the bay and Mount Baker, plus hot tub hookup! The oversized primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet and en suite bathroom. This home also has a private two-car garage, patio, RV parking, and a bonus flex area ideal for a home office or hobby space.This 2-unit building is nestled in a peaceful Anacortes neighborhood with a gorgeous yard!
